{
  "description": "A thick, coiled blue rope hangs against a corrugated metal wall. The rope is tightly wound and appears to be made of braided synthetic fibers. A small portion of red fiber is visible within the coil. The metal wall consists of horizontal ridges and is a muted gray color. The lighting is flat and even, casting minimal shadows. The rope is secured by a knot at the top, creating a loop for hanging. The overall composition is simple and focuses on the texture of the rope and the industrial background.",
